396
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:58,600
You look at that tower and you say,

397
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,100
that tower is good for one thing,

398
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,480
dropping things off.

399
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:03,060
Now,

400
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:03,800
I don't know,

401
00:14:03,860 --> 00:14:05,090
maybe the Doge or whoever they

