00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:06,760
said,

404
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:07,000
no,

405
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:07,240
no,

406
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:07,840
Galileo,

407
00:14:07,860 --> 00:14:09,360
you can't drop things from the tower,

