00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:13,920
but he must have surely thought of it.

411
00:14:15,060 --> 00:14:15,840
All right,

412
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,580
so,

413
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:17,500
the result,

414
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,340
had he done it,

415
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:20,550
and had he not had

416
00:14:20,550 --> 00:14:22,240
to worry about such spurious effects

417
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,380
as air resistance,

418
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:27,080
would be that a cannonball and a feather

