00:14:30,680 --> 00:14:32,120
independent of the mass,

421
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:35,220
and the equation would just say,

422
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,960
the acceleration would first of all be downward,

423
00:14:38,220 --> 00:14:39,260
that's the minus sign,

424
00:14:39,260 --> 00:14:42,260
and equal to this constant G.

425
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:45,580
Excuse me,

