00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,920
Lasers and optical detectors of some sort.

534
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,760
I was just looking at the view.

535
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:47,580
What's that?

536
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:47,880
Oh,

537
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,560
you could certainly tell

538
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,860
if you were standing on the floor here,

539
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,720
you could tell that something was falling toward you.

540
00:18:52,040 --> 00:18:53,200
But the question is,

541
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:55,580
from within this object by itself,

542
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:57,240
without looking at the floor,

543
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:58,420
without knowing the floor was...

544
00:18:58,420 --> 00:19:00,320
Something that wasn't moving is still moving.

