552
00:19:14,640 --> 00:19:16,710
like a beam or a tower

553
00:19:16,710 --> 00:19:18,780
of some sort holding it up.

554
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:19,600
Why?

555
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:21,140
Because this object,

556
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,080
if there are no other forces on it,

557
00:19:23,120 --> 00:19:24,660
only the gravitational forces,

558
00:19:25,320 --> 00:19:28,760
it will fall at the same rate as this.

559
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:30,180
All right.

560
00:19:30,220 --> 00:19:32,440
So that's another expression of the equivalence principle

561
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:35,260
that you cannot tell the difference

562
00:19:35,979 --> 00:19:37,980
between being in free space,

563
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:40,160
