00:20:18,237 --> 00:20:18,797
Well,

586
00:20:18,797 --> 00:20:20,777
we can tell when we're accelerating.

587
00:20:22,337 --> 00:20:22,737
No,

588
00:20:22,737 --> 00:20:24,877
you can't tell when you're accelerating.

589
00:20:25,237 --> 00:20:25,457
Well,

590
00:20:25,457 --> 00:20:27,617
you can't feel that you're accelerating.

591
00:20:27,637 --> 00:20:29,167
Isn't that because there's a

592
00:20:29,167 --> 00:20:30,697
connection between the different objects?

593
00:20:30,777 --> 00:20:31,017
Okay,

594
00:20:31,017 --> 00:20:32,117
here's what you can't tell.

595
00:20:32,917 --> 00:20:33,997
If you go up to

596
00:20:33,997 --> 00:20:35,077
the top of a high building,

597
00:20:35,977 --> 00:20:37,237
and you close your eyes,

598
00:20:37,237 --> 00:20:38,317
and you step off,

599
00:20:38,377 --> 00:20:39,497
and go into free fall,

600
00:20:39,497 --> 00:20:41,997
you will feel exactly the same.

601
00:20:42,037 --> 00:20:42,757
You'll feel weird.

602
00:20:43,057 --> 00:20:43,357
I mean,

603
00:20:43,357 --> 00:20:44,877
that's not the way you usually feel,

604
00:20:44,877 --> 00:20:47,407
because your stomach will come

605
00:20:47,407 --> 00:20:49,937
up and do some funny things.

606
00:20:50,317 --> 00:20:52,377
You might lose it.

607
00:20:52,657 --> 00:20:55,877
But the point is,

608
00:20:55,877 --> 00:20:58,297
you would feel exactly the same discomfort

609
00:20:58,717 --> 00:20:59,737
in outer space,

610
00:20:59,737 --> 00:21:01,777
far from any gravitating object,

611
00:21:02,077 --> 00:21:03,637
just standing still.

612
00:21:03,897 --> 00:21:06,697
You feel exactly the same peculiar feelings.

613
00:21:08,337 --> 00:21:10,477
What are those peculiar feelings due to?

614
00:21:10,957 --> 00:21:12,277
They're not due to falling.

615
00:21:12,477 --> 00:21:13,577
They're due to not fall.

616
00:21:13,757 --> 00:21:14,117
Well...

617
00:21:15,857 --> 00:21:17,207
They're due to the fact that

618
00:21:17,207 --> 00:21:18,557
when you stand on the Earth here,

619
00:21:18,677 --> 00:21:20,457
there are forces on the bottoms of your feet

620
00:21:20,457 --> 00:21:21,777
which keep you from falling.

621
00:21:23,217 --> 00:21:26,277
And if the Earth suddenly disappeared from under my feet,

