00:22:03,897 --> 00:22:05,567
and that the gravitational field

641
00:22:05,567 --> 00:22:07,237
is not the same in every...

642
00:22:07,657 --> 00:22:09,957
same direction in every point,

643
00:22:10,217 --> 00:22:11,837
and that it varies with height.

644
00:22:12,297 --> 00:22:13,357
That's due...

645
00:22:13,357 --> 00:22:15,697
to the finiteness of the Earth.

