721
00:25:34,077 --> 00:25:35,417
The first experiment,

722
00:25:35,657 --> 00:25:36,757
take a little object here,

723
00:25:37,197 --> 00:25:39,037
and electrically charge it.

724
00:25:39,157 --> 00:25:41,937
You electrically charge it by rubbing it on your sweater.

725
00:25:42,857 --> 00:25:45,497
That doesn't put very much electric charge on it,

726
00:25:45,577 --> 00:25:47,667
but it charges it up

727
00:25:47,667 --> 00:25:49,757
