728
00:25:50,397 --> 00:25:53,357
And then take another object of exactly the same kind,

729
00:25:53,577 --> 00:25:54,457
rub it on your shirt,

730
00:25:54,597 --> 00:25:55,677
and put it over here.

731
00:25:56,557 --> 00:25:57,477
What happens?

732
00:25:57,817 --> 00:25:58,917
They repel.

733
00:25:59,097 --> 00:26:01,877
And the fact that they repel means that

734
00:26:03,277 --> 00:26:05,117
this string will shift,

735
00:26:05,217 --> 00:26:06,037
and you'll see it shift.

736
00:26:07,197 --> 00:26:08,417
Take another example.

737
00:26:09,197 --> 00:26:11,257
Take your little ball there to be iron,

738
00:26:11,817 --> 00:26:13,657
and put a magnet next to it.

739
00:26:17,337 --> 00:26:17,897
Again,

740
00:26:17,897 --> 00:26:22,037
you'll see quite an easily detectable deflection

741
00:26:23,197 --> 00:26:25,897
of the string holding it.

742
00:26:26,897 --> 00:26:27,457
Next.

743
00:26:31,897 --> 00:26:34,837
Take a 10,000 pound weight and put it over here.

744
00:26:37,657 --> 00:26:38,757
Guess what happens?

745
00:26:39,577 --> 00:26:40,137
Undetectable.

746
00:26:40,237 --> 00:26:41,837
You cannot see anything happen.

747
00:26:42,197 --> 00:26:44,697
The gravitational force is much,

748
00:26:44,697 --> 00:26:45,517
much weaker

749
00:26:46,197 --> 00:26:48,737
than most other kinds of forces.

750
00:26:49,277 --> 00:26:51,157
And that's due to the,

751
00:26:51,217 --> 00:26:51,937
or not due to,

752
00:26:52,097 --> 00:26:52,697
but the,

753
00:26:52,697 --> 00:26:53,837
not due to that,

754
00:26:53,997 --> 00:26:55,897
the fact that it's so weak

755
00:26:55,897 --> 00:26:58,757
is encapsulated in this small number here.

756
00:26:59,717 --> 00:27:01,077
Another way to say it

757
00:27:01,077 --> 00:27:02,797
is if you take two masses,

758
00:27:02,877 --> 00:27:04,297
each of one kilo,

759
00:27:04,457 --> 00:27:05,397
not one kilometer,

760
00:27:05,637 --> 00:27:06,757
one kilogram,

761
00:27:07,197 --> 00:27:08,537
a kilogram is a good healthy mass,

762
00:27:08,537 --> 00:27:08,837
right?

763
00:27:08,937 --> 00:27:09,737
A nice chunk of iron.

764
00:27:10,397 --> 00:27:10,877
M,

765
00:27:10,877 --> 00:27:11,357
M,

766
00:27:11,437 --> 00:27:13,897
and you separate them by one meter,

