00:27:14,017 --> 00:27:16,437
then the force between them is just G,

768
00:27:16,657 --> 00:27:20,197
and it's 6.7 times 10 to the minus 11,

769
00:27:20,437 --> 00:27:22,237
the units being Newtons.

770
00:27:23,117 --> 00:27:24,717
So it's a very weak force.

