1507
00:52:34,177 --> 00:52:35,287
with a bump on this side

1508
00:52:35,287 --> 00:52:36,397
and a bump on that side.

1509
00:52:36,537 --> 00:52:36,637
Alright,

1510
00:52:36,637 --> 00:52:38,517
I'm not going to go any more deeply into that,

1511
00:52:38,957 --> 00:52:40,497
that I'm sure you've all seen.

1512
00:52:41,537 --> 00:52:41,977
Okay,

1513
00:52:41,977 --> 00:52:43,877
but let's define now what

1514
00:52:43,877 --> 00:52:45,777
we mean by the gravitational field.

