00:53:22,017 --> 00:53:22,897
I'm saying it's always attractive.

1530
00:53:25,217 --> 00:53:25,657
Alright,

1531
00:53:25,657 --> 00:53:26,357
so you have,

1532
00:53:27,157 --> 00:53:29,147
but what about the other

1533
00:53:29,147 --> 00:53:31,137
guys that are pulling upon him,

1534
00:53:31,137 --> 00:53:32,717
from different directions?

1535
00:53:35,697 --> 00:53:36,217
Well,

1536
00:53:36,217 --> 00:53:37,437
let's suppose there's somebody over here,

1537
00:53:38,257 --> 00:53:39,837
and we're talking about the

1538
00:53:39,837 --> 00:53:41,417
force on this person over here.

1539
00:53:41,837 --> 00:53:42,357
Alright,

1540
00:53:42,357 --> 00:53:45,357
obviously there's one force pushing this way

1541
00:53:45,357 --> 00:53:46,897
and another force pushing that way.

1542
