All right,

2067
01:13:50,517 --> 01:13:52,037
so let's be very specific now.

2068
01:13:52,117 --> 01:13:56,677
I kept the lake having an absolutely uniform height,

2069
01:13:56,917 --> 01:13:59,917
and let's also suppose that the density

2070
01:13:59,917 --> 01:14:00,897
of water...

2071
